            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-10264469",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Improper Handling of Case Sensitivity vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2025-46701) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Improper Handling of Case Sensitivity in the `pathInfo` component of a URI mapped to the CGI servlet. An attacker can bypass security constraints that apply to the `pathInfo` component by exploiting this vulnerability on a case insensitive file system.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.105, 10.1.41, 11.0.7 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Advisory](https://lists.apache.org/thread/xhqqk9w5q45srcdqhogdk04lhdscv30j)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html#Fixed_in_Apache_Tomcat_10.1.41)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html#Fixed_in_Apache_Tomcat_11.0.7)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html#Fixed_in_Apache_Tomcat_9.0.105)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/0f01966eb60015d975525019e12a087f05ebf01a)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/238d2aa54b99f91d1111467e2237d2244c64e558)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/2c6800111e7d8d8d5403c07978ea9bff3db5a5a5)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/8cb95ff03221067c511b3fa66d4f745bc4b0a605)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/8df00018a252baa9497615d6420fb6c10466fa74)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/fab7247d2f0e3a29d5daef565f829f383e10e5e2)\n"
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
                "tags": [
                  "security",
                  "CWE-178",
                  "maven"
                ],
                "cvssv3_baseScore": 6.3,
                "security-severity": "6.3"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-10365122",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "High severity - Allocation of Resources Without Limits or Throttling vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2025-48988) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Allocation of Resources Without Limits or Throttling due to the uniform handling of request parameters and parts in multipart requests. An attacker can craft a malicious request with a large number of parts, which can lead to a Denial of Service.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.106, 10.1.42, 11.0.8 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Thread](https://lists.apache.org/thread/nzkqsok8t42qofgqfmck536mtyzygp18)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/2b0ab14fb55d4edc896e5f1817f2ab76f714ae5e)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/cdde8e655bc1c5c60a07efd216251d77c52fd7f6)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/ee8042ffce4cb9324dfd79efda5984f37bbb6910)\n"
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
                "tags": [
                  "security",
                  "CWE-770",
                  "maven"
                ],
                "cvssv3_baseScore": 8.7,
                "security-severity": "8.7"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-10365310",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Authentication Bypass Using an Alternate Path or Channel vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2025-49125) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Authentication Bypass Using an Alternate Path or Channel due to how `PreResources` or `PostResources` handle pre-resources or post-resources mounted at non-root locations. An attacker can gain unauthorized access to protected resources by crafting requests to unexpected paths that bypass intended security constraints.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.106, 10.1.42, 11.0.8 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Thread](https://lists.apache.org/thread/m66cytbfrty9k7dc4cg6tl1czhsnbywk)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/7617b9c247bc77ed0444dd69adcd8aa48777886c)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/9418e3ff9f1f4c006b4661311ae9376c52d162b9)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/d94bd36fb7eb32e790dae0339bc249069649a637)\n"
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "warning"
              },
              "properties": {
