            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-10674391",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "High severity - Integer Overflow or Wraparound vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2025-52520) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Integer Overflow or Wraparound via file uploads through servlet containers. An attacker can craft malicious multipart/form-data requests with specially crafted Content-Length headers that trigger integer overflow vulnerabilities, potentially bypassing file size restrictions and causing memory exhaustion.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.107, 10.1.43, 11.0.9 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Advisory](https://lists.apache.org/thread/trqq01bbxw6c92zx69kx2mw2qgmfy0o5)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/927d66fbc294cb65242102b817a45fd80834e040)\n"
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
