              }
            },
            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-10676855",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "High severity - Allocation of Resources Without Limits or Throttling vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2025-53506) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Allocation of Resources Without Limits or Throttling via HTTP/2 multiplexing feature. an attacker can trigger resource exhaustion by creating excessive HTTP/2 streams within a single TCP connection.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.107, 10.1.43, 11.0.9 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://lists.apache.org/thread/p09775q0rd185m6zz98krg0fp45j8kr0)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/434772930f362145516dd60681134e7f0cf8115b)\n"
              },
