            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-11798986",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Session Fixation vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2025-55668) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Session Fixation via the `rewrite` valve if enabled for a web application. An attacker can gain unauthorized access to another user's session by crafting a request that allows session fixation.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.106, 10.1.42, 11.0.8 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Thread](https://lists.apache.org/thread/v6bknr96rl7l1qxkl1c03v0qdvbbqs47)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/8621e4c6ba2c916a41eb34cb0f781171ead33fb6)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/90306d971bb8b8393336d893644124fb2ca11d21)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/9c3673ba04009377cb0c81ccb6cf5078aec1aa95)\n"
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
