            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-15307822",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "High severity - Incorrect Authorization vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2026-24734) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Incorrect Authorization when using an OCSP responder. OCSP response verification and freshness checks can be bypassed, allowing certificate revocation to be bypassed.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.114, 10.1.52, 11.0.18 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Mailing List](https://lists.apache.org/thread/292dlmx3fz1888v6v16221kpozq56gml)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/e76e9eaa246f30debd603726d9147a8a8cb5171c)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat-native/commit/69a977dd427ad2a6da0f10aca3872386ee27f681)\n"
              },
