                ],
                "cvssv3_baseScore": 2.3,
                "security-severity": "2.3"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-7430175",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "High severity - Insufficient Session Expiration vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2024-34750) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@10.1.20"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "## Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Insufficient Session Expiration due to an infinite timeout being assigned to an open connection improperly, in `http2/Stream.java`. An attacker can force this situation by sending an HTTP/2 stream with excessive headers, causing an out-of-memory error or exhausting `maxConnections`.\n## Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.90, 10.1.25, 11.0.0-M21 or higher.\n## References\n- [Apache Mailing List](https://lists.apache.org/thread/4kqf0bc9gxymjc2x7v3p7dvplnl77y8l)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/2344a4c0d03e307ba6b8ab6dc8b894cc8bac63f2)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/2afae300c9ac9c0e516e2e9de580847d925365c3)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/9fec9a82887853402833a80b584e3762c7423f5f)\n"
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
                "tags": [
                  "security",
                  "CWE-613",
                  "maven"
                ],
                "cvssv3_baseScore": 8.7,
                "security-severity": "8.7"
              }
